data.description: Please Note: Seller will need a leaseback until possibly June 1, 2024. ASSUMABLE VA LOAN 2.875%.  Discover your perfect home in the gated community of Forest Ridge!  This inviting home offers practical living with a touch of comfort. New Water Heater January 2024; Roof 2018! This living space provides a welcoming atmosphere for everyday living. Unwind & entertain on the huge oversized back patio! The heart of the home, the kitchen, is outfitted with gas cooking, durable granite counters, and custom cabinetry, blending functionality with a touch of style. Neighborhood amenities: pool, basketball court, playground, and walking trails.  Easy access to highways, Randolph AFB, and a variety of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.
